<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- wlạ bnkẖạf mn ạllyạly ạ̉w shm ṭạyr ạ̉w
 bsẖr
 tḥt jnạḥ ạlrb mḥmyyn ndws qlb ạlkẖṭr
 1- wnkẖạf mn ạ̹yh wạ̹ḥnạ ạ̹lhnạ ạlly gẖlb ạlmwt
 lw mrẗ ḍạqt nftkr ywnạn fy bṭn ạlḥwt
 2- wnkẖạf mn ạ̹yh wạlrb wʿdh ạ̹nh lynạ yṣwn
 mn mṣr wsṭ ạldẖl ạ̉nqdẖ sẖʿbh mn frʿwn
 3- lw fjạ̉ẗ ḍạʿ mnk ḥbạybk wmn ạlʿbyd mgẖlwb
 gẖryq fy ạ̉rḍk byn dẖkryạtk ạftkr ạ̉ywb
 4- lw ḥty̱ syf ạlsẖr ṣạbk ạfrḥ dạ rbḥ ạ̉kyd
 mʿ ạlmsyḥ kạnt ḥyạtk wạlmwt dạ ywm ạlʿyd</lyrics>
<title>wlạ bnkẖạf mn ạllyạly</title>
